{
  "stem": "9987.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they knew me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when I came back, there was a Gestapo man.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "His name was Becker.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was waiting for me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said, hey, Shlomo, get your coat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Let's go.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he took me in to the Gestapo office.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They treated me quite well there, because they didn't know-- The Gestapo commandant asked me, what happened to you?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Why did you run away?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Why did you escape?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I says-- what did you do?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I says, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I says, I was arrested and I don't know why.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and then after I got beaten up, I saw a possibility to run away, so I escaped.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anyway, he says, you're not going to escape anymore.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Put on handcuffs, put me in a car, and he drove me to the next town, which was called Jaslo, about 20 kilometers away.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had over there a political prison, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] for a Gestapo political prison.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was put in that prison in a cell together with approximately 10 or 12 Polish political prisoners.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "One of them was a Catholic priest.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They did their prayers three days a-- therr three times a day, Catholic, Roman Catholic prayers.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I learned during that time-- approximately six months I was there in prison, no interviews, no nothing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I learned everything what has to do with the Roman Catholic religion, what you do in the morning, how you cross yourself, what you-- what kind of prayer you say noontime, what kind of a prayer you say in the evening, what you do on Christmas, what do you do on-- what you do on Easter.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I was quite versed in the-- in the customs of the Catholic religion.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that was probably my salvation.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
